  <summary date="2023-08-10T14:30:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Electric Vehicles for All Act or the EVs for All Act

This bill requires the Department of Energy to provide grants to eligible entities (i.e., public housing agencies, local governments, and certain non-profit organizations) to facilitate electric vehicle sharing services operated at public housing projects.</summary>
